{"tid":1486423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果尋日係和理非嘅典範，咁目前為止邊一役係勇武嘅典範？往後戰役衝衝子應該以咩做目標","createTime":"2019-08-19T01:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T03:16:28.000Z","uid":31215,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"322dafcd7b037c72a308d2e8666aa0e0521ec0f2","tid":1486423,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"612 包圍立法會<br />\n71 爆入立法會，破壞重要政府機關<br />\n兩次包圍狗屋<br />\n圍稅局接放工癱瘓政府機關<br />\n沙田衝突，打陣地戰但打到可以還擊<br />\n中聯辦一役，污衊大陸象徵圖騰<br />\n85塞鐵加堵路，全港性癱瘓<br />\n811全港性癱瘓兼導致警察引起民憤式嘅犯錯<br />\n812和理非式癱瘓機場不在此列<br />\n813主動癱瘓機場<br />\n<br />\n勇武派其實呢兩三個月都做左好多野<br />\n有啲成果不錯，但有啲做完就要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家我地得到下一次行動升級嘅正當性<br />\n但應該以邊種形式勇武會比較理想？<br />\n塞鐵？塞機場？全港性堵路？癱瘓政府部門？定引到對方犯錯就ok?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beccf695e354658c8fced4746957a5cf0c6fd88b","tid":1486423,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:06:28.000Z","msg":"以上全部"},{"pid":"be0271e3b992f36d471c68d8ae19f757a80beeb7","tid":1486423,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"beccf695e354658c8fced4746957a5cf0c6fd88b","tid":1486423,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:06:28.000Z","msg":"以上全部"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"其中嘅陣地戰送頭率極高<br />\n係咪仲值得玩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367d81f9c6e6ead3f6ae5407fbd235ae04b5fa12","tid":1486423,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru