:"2019-08-19T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"定短暫接管紅隧<br />\n一邊封曬走唔到<br />\n一邊可以免費過海"},{"pid":"f212d49d3349d1541b382e1599821ee501a7dcdb","tid":1486423,"uid":125508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:42:47.000Z","msg":"71真心大勝"},{"pid":"921f1f4fe78aa63da6a256380620d01e961e8157","tid":1486423,"uid":114801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:46:42.000Z","msg":"深水埗燒街衣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙田新城市唯一肉搏，其實好震奮人心，但可惜有人被捕（33個百步梯）"},{"pid":"232400ad117cc0391f96bf102d645080affabaa8","tid":1486423,"uid":209390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:47:43.000Z","msg":"85果日勢最勁<br />\n另名葵芳同黃大仙街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5d124d67faec708b3afd35da9303e63ae42aa0","tid":1486423,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"突然轉去中聯辦呢個決定最精彩。<br />\n但之後同一晚撤退得不爽快亦係最敗筆。"},{"pid":"adc8f4e15d145bce007b454bd490dae5dfc8cbfe","tid":1486423,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3709f70f96b8b90ffdd678234af79c2e127e3dd","tid":1486423,"uid":133765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"0被補又引到d狗出錯既最優先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:56:17.000Z","msg":"呢個其實好難<br />\n引popo出錯好多時都係伴隨住犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0cd7b8b095cea3d3f0f86ce261b18d3bb19d0c","tid":1486423,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"71如果唔係幾位義士見光要離港我覺得算最成功，上午勇武開始進攻，下午和理非行完做援軍，攻入立會後龍和同夏愨道守後路比入面逃走，真係合作無間"},{"pid":"aab2bb5574c4862c6833094b9c674cb23a9ff40e","tid":1486423,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a5d124d67faec708b3afd35da9303e63ae42aa0","tid":1486423,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"突然轉去中聯辦呢個決定最精彩。<br />\n但之後同一晚撤退得不爽快亦係最敗筆。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:00:34.000Z","msg":"嗰時爭個階段性目標 <br />\n一掉完國徽其實走得<br />\n但漫無目的，就會變成迫不得已先走，咁就走得太遲同唔清脆<br />\n<br />\n之後啲hit and run 進化左，因為大家知目標係乜做完走得<br />\n好似塞紅隧，攔哂路就算任務完成，呢個時候走就時間充裕"},{"pid":"55916ed8e90506620b5449aa34dc74e7eaa036d4","tid":1486423,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:02:30.000Z","msg":"Hit &amp; run only"},{"pid":"1366869c5e3153d71f31c7627a6488b9c8fdf404","tid":1486423,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3724b53cda13ae782ff493ab7b884479b097e662","tid":1486423,"uid":199501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:23:02.000Z","msg":"hit&amp;run暫時好似0被捕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45dbf7b32a534ce2e7ea85dfa7f781c1713a909","tid":1486423,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"232400ad117cc0391f96bf102d645080affabaa8","tid":1486423,"uid":209390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:47:43.000Z","msg":"85果日勢最勁<br />\n另名葵芳同黃大仙街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:04:05.000Z","msg":"街坊角色其實越黎越重要了<br />\n近來幾次都係<br />\n勇武打到去某平民區，block 好路，popo出現，勇武自己走<br />\n然後街坊守同屌popo<br />\n因為街坊好難告得入，所以比較安全<br />\n效果上又做到hit and run 同陣地戰嘅融合"},{"pid":"395ca918000f1f857db4db205ebfa5ec56244fc3","tid":1486423,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"71，84，85，817呢4場講真係打得最好，真係唔該keep住呢個勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880d4f7a6fa9572612f5c362cacaad5fbeb1f18a","tid":1486423,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1366869c5e3153d71f31c7627a6488b9c8fdf404","tid":1486423,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3724b53cda13ae782ff493ab7b884479b097e662","tid":1486423,"uid":199501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:2